  political donations.

00:03:36.249 --> 00:03:37.450
Her lottery winnings bought her

00:03:37.450 --> 00:03:38.885
 a reading room named after her

00:03:38.885 --> 00:03:41.387
   at Washington University's
   law school, and millions

00:03:41.387 --> 00:03:44.524
