  to the Democratic Party.

00:03:44.524 --> 00:03:45.792
Eventually, after a decade-long

00:03:45.792 --> 00:03:49.295
 generosity spree, she
 filed for bankruptcy.

00:03:49.295 --> 00:03:52.765 align:start position:0% line:0%
   And number one is spending
   all of your winnings.

00:03:52.765 --> 00:03:54.834 align:start position:0%
